<h1>Apples</h1>
<p>Apples are one of the most popular fruits worldwide. They come in many varieties and are used in a wide range of dishes and drinks.</p>
<ul>
<li>Red Delicious – sweet and crisp.</li>
<li>Granny Smith – tart and firm.</li>
<li>Golden Delicious – mellow and sweet.</li>
<li>Fuji – crunchy and juicy.</li>
<li>Honeycrisp – exceptionally crisp.</li>
</ul>
<button id="factBtn">Show random apple fact</button>
<p id="fact"></p>
<script>
const facts=[
"Apples float in water because 25% of their volume is air.",
"An apple tree can live up to 200 years.",
"Apples are a member of the rose family.",
"Apple trees bloom in early spring, often before the leaves appear.",
"The world’s largest apple was grown in Poland and weighed 4.6 kg (10 lbs)."
];
document.getElementById('factBtn').addEventListener('click',()=>{
const randomFact=facts[Math.floor(Math.random()*facts.length)];
document.getElementById('fact').textContent=randomFact;
});
</script>
